# Intentionally empty.
#
# The ratings/ directory is part of the Phase 2 validation scaffold
# (test_validation_scaffolding.py::test_scaffolding_dirs_present
# pins its existence). External raters contribute rating YAML files
# into this directory, which the harness then consumes. The
# directory is tracked in git so the scaffold is reproducible on a
# fresh clone; this .gitkeep is the only artifact until ratings
# land.
